revision.text:
'''Ablation Casting''' is a variation of [[sand casting]], with a [[soluble]] [[binder (material)|binder]].  The [[mold]] is dissolved and washed away, allowing rapid cooling of the casting.<ref>{{cite web|last=Grassi|first=J|title=The Ablation Casting Process|url=http://www.scientific.net/MSF.618-619.591.pdf|accessdate=6 December 2012}}</ref>

