{{Infobox company | name = ACTIVA | logo = Activa_logo.png | caption = | type = Natural Skin Beauty and Wellness | fate = | predecessor = | successor = | foundation = 1965 | defunct = | location_city = | location_country = | location = Singapore | locations = | area_served = | key_people = | industry = | products = Skin Beauty and Wellness | services = | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | market capitalisation = | aum = | assets = | equity = | owner = | num_employees = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = | homepage = | footnotes = | intl = }}
'''Activa''' is a proprietary brand under Kino Biotech Co. Ltd., a public listed company<ref>[http://www.otc.org.tw/en/regular_emerging/corporateInfo/regular/regular_stock_detail.php?stk_code=4154], Stock Information For Code 4154</ref> in the Taiwan's GreTai Securities Market (GTSM)<ref>[http://www.otc.org.tw/en/about/introduction/history.php], History of Taiwan's Gretal Securities Market</ref> with its head office in Singapore. Kino Biotech Co. Ltd. owns 100% stakes in Kino Life Science Ltd, TRN Marketing (M) Sdn. Bhd. and TRN Marketing Pte. Ltd. The Taiwan's GTSM database of public listed companies states that Kino Biotech Co. Ltd. has over 4500 points of sales in [[China]], [[Singapore]], [[Malaysia]], [[Vietnam]], [[Thailand]] and [[Indonesia]].<ref>[http://www.kinobiotech.com/distribution-networks] Distribution Networks Information For Kino Biotech Co. Ltd.</ref> Their core brands distributed are [[Kinohimitsu]], Activa and Xpertise. Kino Biotech Co. Ltd. offers beauty and wellness [[solution]]s combining both external and internal uses. The Activa brand approaches skin's wellness and beauty (topical use) through natural ingredients.{{what|date=July 2014}} Whereas, its [[Kinohimitsu]] brand targets beauty solution from within our body system.{{what|date=July 2014}} Other global beauty players that offer such external and internal beauty and wellness [[solution]]s are Shishedo, Meiji and DHC brands.
Activa is distributed in malls similar to other players such as ROC<ref>[http://www.rocskincare.com], RoC Skin Care web site</ref> and Avene.<ref>[http://www.eau-thermale-avene.com], Avene web site</ref> The channel of distributions include [[beauty salon]]s, and [[pharmacy|pharmacies]] such as Watson,<ref>[[AS Watson]] [[AS Watson|Watson]]</ref><ref>[[Mannings]] [[Mannings|Guardian Pharmacy]]</ref> Century, Sasa.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sasa.com/SasaWeb/splash.jsp |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2012-04-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120414042439/http://www.sasa.com/SasaWeb/splash.jsp |archivedate=2012-04-14 |df= }} Sasa Retails Information</ref>
